WORLD CUP
FINAL V HUNGARY
Section::::FIFA World Cup finals .
Section::::1954
World Cup
Final v Hungary .
Only 14 days before the final , Germany played the favoured Hungarian Golden Team in the first round of the tournament and suffered a 3 - 8 loss , their highest World Cup defeat to this day .
In the final , Hungary was up by two goals after only eight minutes , so it came as a surprise that the German team not only quickly equalized but turned the game around in the 84th minute with a goal scored by Helmut Rahn .
