TOP GOALSCORERS Section::::Top goalscorers .
Since 2014 , Miroslav Klose is the all - time top goalscorer at FIFA World Cup final tournaments .
Gerd Müller used to be the holder of that record from 1974 until it was broken by Ronaldo in 2006 . !
